GLOBAL.CSS:
    *: Applies reset styles to all elements (sets margin, padding, and box-sizing).

    body: Defines global styles for the entire site, including font size, family, background, and color.


HEADER.CSS:
    .navbar: Styles the navigation bar, fixed to the top of the page.

    .logo: Styles the brand/logo within the header.


NAVITEMSANDSEARCH.CSS:
    .navitems: Styles the navigation menu items.

    .navitems li: Styles individual items within the navigation menu.

    .navitems li a: Styles links within the navigation menu.

    .search: Styles the search container.

    .search-input: Styles the search input field.

    .search-button: Styles the search button.


BANNER.CSS:
    .banner img: Styles images within the banner, ensuring they span the full width.


MEDIA.CSS:
    Media Query (@media screen and (max-width: 1000px)): Applies styles for screens with a maximum width of 1000 pixels.


PRODUCT.CSS
    .product-all: Styles the container for displaying all products.

    .product: Styles individual product cards.

    .product .product-title and .product .product-price: Styles the title and price within product cards.

    .product img: Styles images within product cards, including a hover effect.

    .product a:link and .product a:visited: Styles links within product cards.


TABLE.CSS
    .table-row: Styles a table row with flex properties.

    .table-cell: Styles a table cell with flex properties, padding, and border.
